  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p><img src=\"https://github.com/ollama/ollama/assets/251292/62507173-9423-4496-87ea-7d48be78979c\" width=\"480\"/></p>\n\n<p>Stable LM 2 1.6B is a state-of-the-art 1.6 and 12B billion parameter small language model trained on multilingual data in English, Spanish, German, Italian, French, Portuguese, and Dutch.</p>\n\n<p>The model is trained on a mix of publicly available datasets and synthetic datasets, utilizing Direct Preference Optimization (DPO).</p>\n\n<h2>References</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://stability.ai/news/introducing-stable-lm-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">Announcement</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/stabilityai\" rel=\"nofollow\">HuggingFace</a></p>\n\n        \n      ",
